/* Flexible box model classes */
/* Taken from Alex Russell http://infrequently.org/2009/08/css-3-progress/ */
/* This file is a compatability layer. It allows the usage of flexible box
model layouts accross multiple browsers, including older browsers. The newest,
universal implementation of the flexible box model is used when available (see
`Modern browsers` comments below). Browsers that are known to implement this
new spec completely include:
Firefox 28.0+
Chrome 29.0+
Internet Explorer 11+
Opera 17.0+
Browsers not listed, including Safari, are supported via the styling under the
`Old browsers` comments below.
*/
.hbox {
/* Old browsers */
display: -webkit-box;
-webkit-box-orient: horizontal;
-webkit-box-align: stretch;
display: -moz-box;
-moz-box-orient: horizontal;
-moz-box-align: stretch;
display: box;
box-orient: horizontal;
box-align: stretch;
/* Modern browsers */
display: flex;
flex-direction: row;
align-items: stretch;
}
.hbox > * {
/* Old browsers */
-webkit-box-flex: 0;
-moz-box-flex: 0;
box-flex: 0;
/* Modern browsers */
flex: none;
}
.vbox {
/* Old browsers */
display: -webkit-box;
-webkit-box-orient: vertical;
-webkit-box-align: stretch;
display: -moz-box;
-moz-box-orient: vertical;
-moz-box-align: stretch;
display: box;
box-orient: vertical;
box-align: stretch;
/* Modern browsers */
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: stretch;
}
.vbox > * {
/* Old browsers */
-webkit-box-flex: 0;
-moz-box-flex: 0;
box-flex: 0;
/* Modern browsers */
flex: none;
}
.hbox.reverse,
.vbox.reverse,
.reverse {
/* Old browsers */
-webkit-box-direction: reverse;
-moz-box-direction: reverse;

<h2 id="&#20316;&#19994;-1.1-&#35745;&#31639;Bragg-curve">&#20316;&#19994; 1.1 &#35745;&#31639;Bragg curve<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#20316;&#19994;-1.1-&#35745;&#31639;Bragg-curve">&#182;</a></h2><h3 id="&#26085;&#26399;">&#26085;&#26399;<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#26085;&#26399;">&#182;</a></h3><ul>
<li>限期一周</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="&#35201;&#27714;">&#35201;&#27714;<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#35201;&#27714;">&#182;</a></h3><p>计算质子和$^{12}C$在水中的Bragg curve。分别调节质子和$^{12}C$的入射能量，使两者在水中的Bragg peak 都位于127mm处，Bragg curve的横轴单位取mm，纵轴单位取 MeV/mm。
两种粒子的曲线画在一张图上。</p>
<h4 id="&#25353;&#29031;&#20004;&#31181;&#26041;&#27861;&#35745;&#31639;&#65292;&#27604;&#36739;&#20004;&#31181;&#26041;&#27861;&#24471;&#21040;&#30340;&#32467;&#26524;">&#25353;&#29031;&#20004;&#31181;&#26041;&#27861;&#35745;&#31639;&#65292;&#27604;&#36739;&#20004;&#31181;&#26041;&#27861;&#24471;&#21040;&#30340;&#32467;&#26524;<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#25353;&#29031;&#20004;&#31181;&#26041;&#27861;&#35745;&#31639;&#65292;&#27604;&#36739;&#20004;&#31181;&#26041;&#27861;&#24471;&#21040;&#30340;&#32467;&#26524;">&#182;</a></h4><ol>
<li><p>将材料切成厚度很小的薄片，此时可认为在薄片内dE/dx为常数</p>
<ul>
<li>能量为E的粒子穿过一个厚度为厚度$\Delta x_i$的材料后,能量损失$\Delta E_i$为，
$$
\Delta E_i=\frac{dE}{dx}(E) \cdot \Delta x_i
$$</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>粒子每经过一个切片,剩余能量为$E=E-\Delta E_i$, 穿过的厚度为：$x=\sum_i{\Delta x_i}$。由此得到Bragg curve上的一个点的坐标(x, $\frac{dE}{dx}(E)$)。以此类推，直至$E \to 0$。</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<ol>
<li>假设粒子在材料中每次损失很小的固定能损$\Delta E$<ul>
<li>能量为E的粒子的粒子损失$\Delta E$的能量时，穿过的材料厚度$\Delta x$为，
$$
\Delta x=\frac{\Delta E}{\frac{dE}{dx}(E)}
$$</li>
<li>求出每一步的剩余能量$E$和穿过的材料厚度$x$，得到Bragg curve上的一个点的坐标(x, $\frac{dE}{dx}(E)$)。以此类推，直至能量$E'\to 0$</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="&#39044;&#26399;&#25928;&#26524;">&#39044;&#26399;&#25928;&#26524;<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#39044;&#26399;&#25928;&#26524;">&#182;</a></h3><p><img src="result.png" alt=""></p>
<h3 id="&#26399;&#38480;">&#26399;&#38480;<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#26399;&#38480;">&#182;</a></h3><ul>
<li>至发布之日起两周内提交</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<li>作业1.1和作业1.2都可以从以下代码扩展得到。</li>
<li>如果在ROOT平台上运行，按照下列步骤执行<ul>
<li>下载 <a href="srimc.C">SRIM-dE/dx</a> 或 <a href="lisec.C">Lise-dE/dx</a></li>
<li>在ROOT上运行 root -l xx.C</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>在jupyter内运行下列代码</li>
</ul>

<span class="n">ifstream</span> <span class="n">inf</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">elossfile</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="c1">//读入LISE软件生成的12C入射到H2O的数据</span>
<span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">inf</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">is_open</span><span class="p">()){</span> <span class="c1">//文件不存时。。</span>
<span class="n">cout</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;Data File: &quot;</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">elossfile</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="s">&quot; does not exist!&quot;</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">endl</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="k">return</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
<span class="k">auto</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">g</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="k">new</span> <span class="n">TGraph</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">//定义新的二维散点图(TGraph) g</span>
<span class="n">string</span> <span class="n">ss</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="n">string</span> <span class="n">sunit</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">//能量单位</span>
<span class="kt">double</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">ededx</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ndedx</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">//ededx-电子阻止本领，ndedx-核阻止本领 </span>
<span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="k">for</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">j</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">j</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="mi">24</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">j</span><span class="o">++</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">getline</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">inf</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">ss</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="c1">//读入文件中开始的24行描述性文本</span>
<span class="k">while</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">inf</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">sunit</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">ededx</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">ndedx</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">ss</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">ss</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">ss</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="p">{</span>
<span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">abs</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="mf">1.0e-4</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">break</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">//对于非数据，e值为零，此时停止读数据</span>
<span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sunit</span><span class="o">==</span><span class="s">&quot;keV&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="o">/=</span><span class="mf">1e3</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sunit</span><span class="o">==</span><span class="s">&quot;GeV&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">e</span> <span class="o">*=</span> <span class="mf">1e3</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="n">g</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">SetPoint</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">++</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ededx</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">ndedx</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="c1">//在g1中加入点, 参考TGraph class reference 中 SetPoint()函数用法</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
<span class="n">inf</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">();</span>
<span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">g</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
